div.div: Ling Jian Chen, the master of the God-Emperor, is reborn as a mortal and he has started an unbeatable life that defeats everyone against him! Genius? Even the God-Emperor is my student. Talking about genius and masters? Even the God-Emperor serves me with respect in order to receive my words of guidance, are you as unbeatable as me? Beauties? Have you ever heard of the most beautiful goddess in the Divine Realm? She has tried everything to stay with me ... Everyone in heaven, listen to my orders, I'm the one and the only in all the eight realms in heaven.
Ben Xu Xiu de Shi Jian Dao

In my previous life, I was forced to cultivate for a hundred years by a ruthless empress. I severed my soul just to escape from that tiger's den! In this life, I'll learn all the martial arts and soul techniques so that I can change this perilous world! (Source: Bilibili Comics, translated)
